{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "easyvtc-favorites-sprint6",
    "name": "EasyVTC API — Destinations Favorites (Sprint 6)",
    "description": "# EasyVTC — Module Destinations Favorites\n\n## Endpoints couverts\n- `GET    /users/:id/favorites`          → Lister les favoris (client soi-même ou admin)\n- `POST   /users/:id/favorites`          → Ajouter un favori (max 20 par client)\n- `DELETE /users/:id/favorites/:favId`   → Supprimer un favori\n\n## Logique métier\n- Seul le client propriétaire ou un admin peut accéder aux favoris\n- Maximum 20 favoris par utilisateur (erreur 422 si dépassé)\n- Les coordonnées GPS (`lat`, `lng`) sont optionnelles\n\n## Variables sauvegardées\n- `admin_token`, `client_token`, `driver_token`\n- `client_user_id`\n- `fav_id_1`, `fav_id_2`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url",       "value": "http://localhost:4000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "admin_token",    "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "client_token",   "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "driver_token",   "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "client_user_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "fav_id_1",       "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "fav_id_2",       "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [

    {
      "name": "🔐 Setup — Tokens",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login Admin",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["auth","login"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin1234!\"\n}" }
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
            "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
            "const { ok, data } = pm.response.json();",
            "pm.expect(ok).to.be.true;",
            "pm.collectionVariables.set('admin_token', data.access_token);"
          ]}}]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login Client — récupère client_user_id",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["auth","login"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"client@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Client1234!\"\n}" }
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
            "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
            "const { ok, data } = pm.response.json();",
            "pm.expect(ok).to.be.true;",
            "pm.collectionVariables.set('client_token', data.access_token);",
            "pm.collectionVariables.set('client_user_id', data.user.id);",
            "console.log('client_user_id:', data.user.id);"
          ]}}]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login Driver",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["auth","login"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"driver@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Driver1234!\"\n}" }
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
            "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
            "const { ok, data } = pm.response.json();",
            "pm.collectionVariables.set('driver_token', data.access_token);"
          ]}}]
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "name": "⭐ Client — Gestion des favoris",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "① GET /users/:id/favorites — liste initiale (vide)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{client_token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/users/{{client_user_id}}/favorites",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["users","{{client_user_id}}","favorites"]
            }
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
            "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
            "pm.test('Tableau de favoris retourné', () => {",
            "  const { ok, data } = pm.response.json();",
            "  pm.expect(ok).to.be.true;",
            "  pm.expect(data).to.be.an('array');",
            "  console.log('Favoris existants:', data.length);",
            "});"
          ]}}]
        },
        {
          "name": "② POST — Ajouter favori 1 (avec coordonnées GPS)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{client_token}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/users/{{client_user_id}}/favorites",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["users","{{client_user_id}}","favorites"]
            },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"label\": \"Domicile\",\n  \"address\": \"12 rue de la Paix, 75001 Paris\",\n  \"lat\": 48.8698,\n  \"lng\": 2.3309\n}" }
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
            "pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
            "pm.test('Favori créé avec coordonnées', () => {",
            "  const { ok, data } = pm.response.json();",
            "  pm.expect(ok).to.be.true;",
            "  pm.expect(data.label).to.equal('Domicile');",
            "  pm.expect(data.address).to.be.a('string');",
            "  pm.expect(data.lat).to.equal(48.8698);",
            "  pm.expect(data.lng).to.equal(2.3309);",
            "  pm.expect(data.id).to.be.a('string');",
            "  pm.collectionVariables.set('fav_id_1', data.id);",
            "  console.log('fav_id_1:', data.id, '|', data.label);",
            "});"
          ]}}]
        },
        {
          "name": "② POST — Ajouter favori 2 (sans coordonnées)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{client_token}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/users/{{client_user_id}}/favorites",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["users","{{client_user_id}}","favorites"]
            },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"label\": \"Bureau\",\n  \"address\": \"Tour Montparnasse, 33 Avenue du Maine, 75015 Paris\"\n}" }
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
            "pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
            "pm.test('Favori créé sans coordonnées', () => {",
            "  const { ok, data } = pm.response.json();",
            "  pm.expect(ok).to.be.true;",
            "  pm.expect(data.label).to.equal('Bureau');",
            "  pm.expect(data.lat).to.be.null;",
            "  pm.expect(data.lng).to.be.null;",
            "  pm.collectionVariables.set('fav_id_2', data.id);",
            "  console.log('fav_id_2:', data.id, '|', data.label);",
            "});"
          ]}}]
        },
        {
          "name": "③ GET /users/:id/favorites — liste après ajouts",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{client_token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/users/{{client_user_id}}/favorites",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["users","{{client_user_id}}","favorites"]
            }
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
            "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
            "pm.test('2 favoris minimum dans la liste', () => {",
            "  const { ok, data } = pm.response.json();",
            "  pm.expect(ok).to.be.true;",
            "  pm.expect(data.length).to.be.at.least(2);",
            "  const ids = data.map(f => f.id);",
            "  pm.expect(ids).to.include(pm.collectionVariables.get('fav_id_1'));",
            "  pm.expect(ids).to.include(pm.collectionVariables.get('fav_id_2'));",
            "  console.log('Favoris:', data.map(f => f.label).join(', '));",
            "});"
          ]}}]
        },
        {
          "name": "④ DELETE — Supprimer favori 2 (Bureau)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{client_token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/users/{{client_user_id}}/favorites/{{fav_id_2}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["users","{{client_user_id}}","favorites","{{fav_id_2}}"]
            }
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
            "pm.test('Status 200 — supprimé', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
            "pm.test('ok = true', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().ok).to.be.true);",
            "pm.collectionVariables.set('fav_id_2', '');"
          ]}}]
        },
        {
          "name": "⑤ GET — Vérification suppression (fav_id_2 absent)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{client_token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/users/{{client_user_id}}/favorites",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["users","{{client_user_id}}","favorites"]
            }
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
            "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
            "pm.test('fav_id_1 toujours présent', () => {",
            "  const { data } = pm.response.json();",
            "  const ids = data.map(f => f.id);",
            "  pm.expect(ids).to.include(pm.collectionVariables.get('fav_id_1'));",
            "  console.log('Favoris restants:', data.length);",
            "});"
          ]}}]
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "name": "👨‍💼 Admin — Accès aux favoris d'un client",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /users/:id/favorites — vue admin",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{admin_token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/users/{{client_user_id}}/favorites",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["users","{{client_user_id}}","favorites"]
            }
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
            "pm.test('Status 200 — admin peut voir les favoris du client', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
            "pm.test('ok = true', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().ok).to.be.true);",
            "const { data } = pm.response.json();",
            "console.log('Favoris du client (vue admin):', data.length);"
          ]}}]
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "name": "🔴 Cas d'erreur",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "[400] POST — label manquant",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{client_token}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/users/{{client_user_id}}/favorites",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["users","{{client_user_id}}","favorites"]
            },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"address\": \"10 rue Test, 75001 Paris\"\n}" }
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
            "pm.test('Status 400 — label requis', () => pm.response.to.have.status(400));",
            "pm.test('ok = false', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().ok).to.be.false);"
          ]}}]
        },
        {
          "name": "[400] POST — adresse trop courte",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{client_token}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/users/{{client_user_id}}/favorites",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["users","{{client_user_id}}","favorites"]
            },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"label\": \"Test\",\n  \"address\": \"ab\"\n}" }
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
            "pm.test('Status 400 — adresse trop courte (min 5 chars)', () => pm.response.to.have.status(400));",
            "pm.test('ok = false', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().ok).to.be.false);"
          ]}}]
        },
        {
          "name": "[404] DELETE — favId inconnu",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{client_token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/users/{{client_user_id}}/favorites/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["users","{{client_user_id}}","favorites","00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"]
            }
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
            "pm.test('Status 404 — favori introuvable', () => pm.response.to.have.status(404));",
            "pm.test('ok = false', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().ok).to.be.false);"
          ]}}]
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "name": "🔒 Contrôle d'accès",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "[401] GET sans token",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/users/{{client_user_id}}/favorites",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["users","{{client_user_id}}","favorites"]
            }
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
            "pm.test('Status 401', () => pm.response.to.have.status(401));"
          ]}}]
        },
        {
          "name": "[403] Driver — GET favoris d'un client",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{driver_token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/users/{{client_user_id}}/favorites",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["users","{{client_user_id}}","favorites"]
            }
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
            "pm.test('Status 403 — driver ne peut pas accéder aux favoris client', () => pm.response.to.have.status(403));"
          ]}}]
        }
      ]
    }

  ]
}
